{"tid":405993,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"寵物鋪沖涼後無左半條尾","createTime":"2017-09-19T09:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T20:14:37.000Z","uid":131115,"like":7,"dislike":117,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"061f5a10b1de1604eac749b6fe820e8f79066068","tid":405993,"uid":131115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:40:13.000Z","msg":"有無人有類似情況？<br />\n寵物鋪話係結太多 （但上個月沖完 我自己又有梳下架喎 !!!!! ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明上個月沖涼都無事<br />\n明明條尾又大又多毛<br />\n明明係挪威森林猫<br />\n⋯<br />\n最後變英短尾 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/173551_82cc75861dbd4cd86db56452b3d501e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F173551_82cc75861dbd4cd86db56452b3d501e8.jpg&h=f8d86e49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/173552_82cc75861dbd4cd86db56452b3d501e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F173552_82cc75861dbd4cd86db56452b3d501e8.jpg&h=1b91d9eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aaeb24f66c72c201d8eb02e3f6beb89bf9f3ac25","tid":405993,"uid":97863,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"似未乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbfb005212f32612dd70ffed43cfea2a92120454","tid":405993,"uid":131115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T09:46:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>似未乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩岩拎返屋企一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f3ed550e480632ce7fb74bdd69f275109be7f4","tid":405993,"uid":97863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:13:32.000Z","msg":"我之前幫主子沖涼都係咁，幫佢沖完涼後以為條尾縮咗水，但兩三日後又係蓬鬆返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你會唔會幫佢剷屎忽d毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368c83d022765e2b82d2a85e3f9b913b982d55cd","tid":405993,"uid":694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:16:26.000Z","msg":"松鼠狗 多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd2b7bd86eaae25d5f4fc0bc4b878869979e904","tid":405993,"uid":131115,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:25:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我之前幫主子沖涼都係咁，幫佢沖完涼後以為條尾縮咗水，但兩三日後又係蓬鬆返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你會唔會幫佢剷屎忽d毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寵物鋪send左一埋毛比我睇😞😞<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/182251_616129e748e4b3b0846027ea55e6dd2d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F182251_616129e748e4b3b0846027ea55e6dd2d.jpg&h=797d3816&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/182529_8dcf381d94c7f9a3f55a4ac3d6144749.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F182529_8dcf381d94c7f9a3f55a4ac3d6144749.jpg&h=89629d19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a6ce07d1dc59c2e4db365afbf98f6d4f866885f","tid":405993,"uid":131115,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>松鼠狗 多圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主子正面圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/182743_7678bc6093dbb6a66380d772ad01f145.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F182743_7678bc6093dbb6a66380d772ad01f145.jpg&h=992a43d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/19/182744_1b0020bfe182c94114b61e02abfb1fa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F19%2F182744_1b0020bfe182c94114b61e02abfb1fa3.jpg&h=958fbd45&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7386a8930f21662d24a52c4864743c08445051a","tid":405993,"uid":97863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"我嗰隻都有打結，我通常都係剪咗打結嗰一忽<br />\n但你個隻似係格硬梳😐⋯（因為我以前都係咁幫主人整，一野梳落去，但佢勁唔開心）"},{"pid":"543b23af65227c7ea025a3eb9627525080a74494","tid":405993,"uid":76105,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"但佢梳出黎 真係打結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通整出黎屈你 or 專登剪佢d毛咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a21a4762bab807431b85e3e45b38a12b11dcec7","tid":405993,"uid":131115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嗰隻都有打結，我通常都係剪咗打結嗰一忽<br />\n但你個隻似係格硬梳😐⋯（因為我以前都係咁幫主人整，一野梳落去，但佢勁唔開心）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 心痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e447f3a48e407bf9f0c7d59f8ab246e5c03c8e6","tid":405993,"uid":131115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但佢梳出黎 真係打結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通整出黎屈你 or 專登剪佢d毛咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以先開po 問有無長毛主子有類似經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d0b5ae3ca9f3e69a16a7a0651c8d2d2a4bcb124","tid":405993,"uid":62050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi